node.text:
"Nothing's gonna hurt you baby" — @cigsaftersex

Huge thanks to @xxmelodi and @justincayton for finally allowing me to bring this mini set into fruition 💙

These lyrics mean something completely different, but I just had to put my own spin on it.

Shot on my a7iii / 35mm 1.8 and edited on Adobe Photoshop 👨🏻‍💻

node.text:
Maybe I'm too emotional 🔥

Credits to @oliviarodrigo's creative team for inspiring me to recreate this

I used 2 LED lights placed where the fire would be, alongside the available natural light in the room. I need to invest in some reflectors though. 🥴

Shot on my a7iii / 35mm 1.8 and edited on Adobe Photoshop 👨🏻‍💻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Calob Castellon on July 03, 2021 tagging @barbieshelly. May be an image of standing, fire, fireworks and text.

node.text:
Sparks fly, its like electricity, I might die 🤕

Haven't used a tripod in so long, but it was necessary to get the lighting right. Using my old method, i combined several different exposures for the look. Tons of running back and forth involved. 🏃🏻‍♀️💥

Shot on a7iii / 35mm 1.8 and edited on Adobe Photoshop 👨🏻‍💻

node.text:
If I'm gonna burn, it might as well be bright 🔥

Sadly couldn't fit my watermark in this set. Like where could it possibly go? 🤨 Anyways, have a great weekend everyone! 

Shot on my a7iii / 35mm 1.8 and single RGB LED

Edited on Adobe Photoshop 👨🏻‍💻

#VFX #artoftheday
